śrīādināthāya namo'stu tasmai yenopadiṣṭā haṭhayogavidyā/ virājate pronnatarājayogam āroḍhum icchor adhirohiṇīva// praṇamya śrīguruṃ nāthaṃ svātmārāmeṇa yoginā/ kevalaṃ rājayogāya haṭhavidyopadiśyate// bhrāntyā bahumatadhvānte rajayogam ajānatām/ haṭhapradīpikāṃ dhatte svātmārāmaḥ kṛpākaraḥ//haṭhavidyā hi matsyendragorakṣādyā vijānate/ svātmārāmo 'thavā yogī jānīte tatprasādataḥ// ādināthamatsyendraśābarānandabhairavāḥ/ cauraṅgīmīnagorakṣavirūpākṣabileśayāḥ// manthānabhairavo yogī śuddhabuddhaś ca kanthariḥ/ pauraṇḍakaḥ surānandaḥ siddhapādaś ca carppaṭiḥ// kāṇerī pūrvapādaś ca dhvaninātho nirañjanaḥ/ kapālī bindunādaś ca kākacaṇḍīśvarādayaḥ // {}prabhudevaś ca ghorāvolā ca ṭiṇṭiṇī / bhālukā nāgabodhaś ca khaṇḍīkāpālikas tathā// ity ādayo mahāsiddhā haṭhayogaprabhāvataḥ / khaṇḍayitvā kāladaṇḍaṃ brahmāṇḍe vicaranti te// saṃsāratāpataptānāṃ samāśrayo haṭho mataḥ/ aśeṣayogajagatām ādhāraḥkamaṭho haṭhaḥ// haṭhavidyā paraṃ gopyā yoginā siddhim icchatā/ bhaved vīryavatī guptā nirvīryā tu prakāśitā// surājye dhārmike deśe subhikṣe nirupadrave/ dhanuḥpramāṇaparyaṃtaṃ śilāgnijalavarjjitaṃ// ekānte maṭhikā madhye sthātavyaṃhaṭha yoginā// alpadvāram arandhragataṃ pīṭhakāṃ nātyuccanīcāyataṃ/ samyag gomayasārdraliptavimalaṃ niḥśeṣaṃjantohiṃtam/ bāhye maṇḍapavedikūparacitaṃ prākārasaṃveṣṭite/ proktaṃ yogamaṭhasya lakṣaṇam idaṃ siddhair haṭhābhyāsibhiḥ// evaṃvidhe maṭhe sthitvā sarvacintā vivarjitaḥ/ gurūpadiṣṭamārgeṇa yogam evaṃ sadābhyaset// atyāhāra prayāsaś ca prajalpo viparyagrahaḥ/ janasaṅgaś ca laulyaṃ ca ṣaḍbhir yogaḥ vinaśyati// utsāhān niścayādvairyyāttattvajñānāc ca niścalāt/ janasaṅgaparityāgāt ṣaḍbhir yogaś ca sidhyati// ahiṃsā satyam asteyaṃ brahmacaryaṃ kṣamā dhṛtiḥ/ dayārjjavamitāhāraḥ śaucaṃ caiva yamā daśāḥ// tapaḥ santoṣa āstikyaṃ dānam iśvarapūjanaṃ/ siddhāntaśravaṇaṃ caiva hrīmatiś ca japo hṛtam// haṭhasya prathamāṅgatvād āsanaṃ pūrvam ucyate/ kuryāt tad āsanaṃ tasmād ārogyaṃ cāṅgapāṭavaṃ// vasiṣṭhādyaiś ca munibhir matsyendrādyaiś ca yogibhiḥ/ aṅgīkṛtānyāsanāni kathyante kānicinmayā// jānūr vorantare samyak kṛtvā pādatalāv ubhau/ ṛjukāyasamāsīnaḥ svastikaṃ tat pracakṣate// savye dakṣiṇagulphaṃ tu pṛṣṭhapārśve niyojayet / dakṣiṇe'pi tathā savyaṃ gomukhaṃ gomukhākṛtiḥ// 